                    <tr>
                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> These guys are really easy. Did 60% of lvl 62 here in a few hours of non stop pulling. Resists are pretty low, you get the occasional resist on dooming, but nothing to worry about. I used SoW potions at all times even though i DO have run3...these bad boys like to hit for 600+ and stun quite often...600+ damage per hit + stun = 400-1kpp down the drain for an EE. At 62 you CAN kill sentries with no worries, they con yellow, but are fairly weak. Cast SK first (to pull) send pet, run to one side of room cast FP, other side of room cast splurt, other side again cast DP then run around in a circle until SK and/or FP wear off (pet can hit sentry at ALL TIMES when running in a circle, makes process a lot faster)</span id="msg"></font></td>
                    </tr>
